ua những mối dây liên kết tưởng như nhỏ bé: tình yêu dành cho thú cưng, sự đồng cảm và khao khát chữa lành. Một câu chuyện tình nhẹ nhàng nhưng sâu sắc, nơi những chú chó trở thành chất xúc tác cho sự kết nối và trưởng thành.<br>&nbsp;</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"290788","season":1,"vote_average":7,"vote_count":2},"modified":"2025-10-19T20:59:57.000Z","cast":["Kaya Kiyohara","Narita Ryo","Na In-woo","Riku Hagiwara","Emma Miyazawa","Kyoko Fukada","Goro Kishitani","Takeshi Nadagi","Kayo Noro","Riko Nagase","Wan Marui","Maki Sakai","Noa Kazama"],"director":["노영섭","岡本伸吾"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Kaya Kiyohara","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kaya Kiyohara","tmdb_id":1671407,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9BoIEdUhkHFhC521us29EqHoti0.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1671407"},{"name":"Narita Ryo","name_vi":"Narita Ryo","name_original":"Ryo Narita","tmdb_id":1668610,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/f42OXn4J7cM62wtykL196YW7x85.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1668610"},{"name":"Na In-woo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Na In-woo","tmdb_id":2935390,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/75rOHTfq7M3E29D88mvYQf1cS0M.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2935390"},{"name":"Riku Hagiwara","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Riku Hagiwara","tmdb_id":1668193,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yX2Zjhy7FdPwLexGxG8sgoSgakN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1668193"},{"name":"Emma Miyazawa","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Emma Miyazawa","tmdb_id":2984998,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iarZIkFoFYofryskxVFJyIEXU56.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2984998"},{"name":"Kyoko Fukada","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kyoko Fukada","tmdb_id":13253,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jQ2UNLzoliUZab6UiO9523TgIi8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/13253"},{"name":"Goro Kishitani","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Goro Kishitani","tmdb_id":43664,"profi